::: {.callout-tip title="Solution"}

The next chunk handles several other parts of the summary. 

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
glance_lm <-  . %$% (
  glance(.) %>% 
  mutate(across(-c(p.value), 
                ~ round(.x, digits=2)),
         p.value=signif(p.value,3)) %>% 
  gt::gt() %>% 
  gt::tab_caption(glue("Dataset: {call$data},  Formula: {deparse(call$formula)}"))
)

glance_lm(lm0)
```

