$$
(X^T \times X)^{-1} = \begin{bmatrix}
0.18 & -0.026 & -0.18 & 0.026\\
-0.026 & 0.0048 & 0.026 & -0.0048\\
-0.18 & 0.026 & 0.31 & -0.048\\
0.026 & -0.0048 & -0.048 & 0.0099
\end{bmatrix}
$$


::: {.content-visible when-profile="solution"}

